<p>Using the 64-bit edition is recommended. As noted above, it can still build 32-bit installers, and does so by default.</p>

<p>To install 64-bit Inno Setup 7 interactively using <tt>winget</tt> use the following command: <tt>winget install --id JRSoftware.InnoSetup.7 -e -s winget -i</tt></p>

